## Basic Usage

::: {#f1de88ad .cell execution_count=4}
``` {.python .cell-code}
def your_decorator(func):
  def wrapper():
    # Do stuff before func...
    print("Before func!")
    func()
    # Do stuff after func...
    print("After func!")
  return wrapper
```
:::


### Decorator

::: {#ebaf2aa4 .cell execution_count=5}
``` {.python .cell-code}
